    "description": "踏上绿茵场，体验<i>Bang Average Football</i>——适合足球迷的终极足球游戏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/7b777e9a3770d79af9bd479d743bf438.poster.avif?t=1763554049\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/7b777e9a3770d79af9bd479d743bf438.webm?t=1763554049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/7b777e9a3770d79af9bd479d743bf438.mp4?t=1763554049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游玩节奏快和机制易于上手等特色的加持下，<i>Bang Average Football</i>堪称适合所有技能水平的完美游戏。从丰富的男女球队中选择你的最爱，在快节奏、充满动作性的比赛中体验足球的激动人心之处。在本地多玩家模式中痛扁你的好友，或是在单玩家剧情模式中追名逐利。凭借简单的操控和令人上瘾的游玩方法，<i>Bang Average Football</i>可带来登峰造极的足球体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/d96e7984f02c755c1945bb4759766947.poster.avif?t=1763554049\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/d96e7984f02c755c1945bb4759766947.webm?t=1763554049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/d96e7984f02c755c1945bb4759766947.mp4?t=1763554049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 以球员经理的身份加入一支跌入谷底的足球俱乐部，带领他们一路高歌猛进，直至荣耀的巅峰！<br></li><li> 学习如何管理你的球队、完成战略性转会、升级本地体育场、签约赞助商并和球迷互动，最大化对俱乐部来说至关重要的声望值。<br></li><li> 在比赛之间拜访全国的其他城市和俱乐部，一路接受挑战来提高你的能力，成为一名配得上全国冠军身份的玩家！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/660122ae614034a83571fe53b7621d2d.poster.avif?t=1763554049\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/660122ae614034a83571fe53b7621d2d.webm?t=1763554049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393770/extras/660122ae614034a83571fe53b7621d2d.mp4?t=1763554049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 本地多玩家模式，适合1-4名玩家。<br></li><li> 25支球队和1,000+ 男女球员。<br></li><li> 丰富的球队和角色创建与定制选择。<br></li><li> 深入的战术定制和控制，包括自定义阵型和球队指示。<br></li><li> 辅助功能设置，包括适合色盲玩家的高对比度模式。</li></ul>",
